details.trait:
When I arrive at a new settlement for the first time, I must learn all its customs. I'm a stickler when it comes to observing proper etiquette and local customs.
I'm especially interested in local recipes and cooking.
details.ideal: Knowledge: By understanding other races and cultures, we learn to understand ourselves. (Any)
details.bond: I have a trinket (crystal) that I believe is the key to finding a long-lost society.
details.flaw:
I've picked up some unpleasant habits living among goblins, like blowing a wad of snot into a stew to improve the flavor.
Terrified of the "sea" (can swim however) - horribly seasick
Believe lots of pseudo-science about crystals
